Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}住得還舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比想像的好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這麼多年為難你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一大早的怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 我們以後就要一起生活了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我覺得一開始就把嚴肅的話說了會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還挺好吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}薄片火腿 用橄欖油稍稍炸一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一般來說孩子因為父母的緣故被迫東奔西跑是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我還沒獨立嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在某種程度上這也是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你能這麼說我就輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是那也得是年齡還小沒辦法自立的孩子才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也可能不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你一直都在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和你在一起就有點不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}算是 一直聽著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也是喜歡聽著媽媽的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}登山回來都已經兩天了 我的腳還在痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 我的腳不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 難道 要住院了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 你已經知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳似乎不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說是不需要住院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉打來電話說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳在練習的時候把腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過是一點扭傷 不用你專門來陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}當然要來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們是一家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼這種臉色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你就會說「沒什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太生分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 小柳 雪哉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你太重了 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哎呀 好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這樣打的嗎 好朋友之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 基本上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 那 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.23,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2}聖艾克絮佩里——《人類的大地》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我來還之前的那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 已經看完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那沙漠公車裡的蒼蠅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這竟然就是未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這麼一想就產生了興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 奇怪的未來我可不想要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}希望我們一直都能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真想看到這樣的未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今後 小柳和小雪會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}別發呆 會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是
